under department rules, said the protesters included ``professional
rowdies who travel around to violently disrupt meetings.''
   Left-wing organizations accuse the Republicans of being
neo-fascist and hostile toward West Germany's millions of foreign
workers and immigrants.
   The party won a surprising 7.5 percent of the vote in West
Berlin elections in January.
